<body>

<header><div class="logo"><span class="blue">Rajaram</span> <span class="green">Finance</span></div></header>

<div class="container">
  
  <!-- 1. INPUT - GOLD LOAN -->
  <div class="card">
    <h2>Gold Loan EMI Calculator</h2>
    <div class="input-group">
      <label>Gold Weight in Grams</label>
      <div class="input-wrapper"><span>g</span><input type="number" id="grams" value="20" oninput="calculateGoldLoan()"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="input-group">
      <label>Gold Rate per Gram ₹</label>
      <div class="input-wrapper"><span>₹</span><input type="number" id="rate" value="7500" oninput="calculateGoldLoan()"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="input-group">
      <label>Loan Amount ₹</label>
      <div class="input-wrapper"><span>₹</span><input type="number" id="amount" value="100000" oninput="calculateGoldLoan()"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="input-group">
      <label>Interest Rate %</label>
      <div class="input-wrapper"><span>%</span><input type="number" id="interest" value="9.5" step="0.1" oninput="calculateGoldLoan()"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="input-group">
      <label>Loan Tenure Months</label>
      <div class="input-wrapper"><span>Mos</span><input type="number" id="months" value="12" oninput="calculateGoldLoan()"></div>
    </div>
    <button class="btn-primary" onclick="calculateGoldLoan()">CALCULATE NOW</button>
  </div>

  <!-- 2. RESULT -->
  <div class="card result-card">
    <div class="label">MONTHLY EMI</div>
    <div class="value" id="emi">₹0</div>
    <div class="label">TOTAL INTEREST</div>
    <div class="value" id="interestAmt">₹0</div>
    <div class="label">TOTAL PAYMENT</div>
    <div class="value" id="total">₹0</div>
    <div class="result-grid">
      <div class="result-mini"><div class="label">GOLD VALUE</div><div class="value" id="goldValue">₹0</div></div>
      <div class="result-mini"><div class="label">LTV</div><div class="value" id="ltv">0%</div></div>
      <div class="result-mini"><div class="label">ELIGIBLE</div><div class="value" id="eligible">₹0</div></div>
    </div>
    <button class="btn-download" id="downloadPdf">📄 Download PDF Report</button>
  </div>

  <!-- 3. GRAPH -->
  <div class="card">
    <h2>Gold Loan Breakdown</h2>
    <canvas id="pieChart" height="120"></canvas>
  </div>

  <!-- 4. GOLD LOAN CONTENT -->
  <div class="card content">
    <h2>What is Gold Loan?</h2>
    <p><b>Gold Loan</b> is a secured loan where you pledge gold jewelry to get money. Banks give up to 75% of gold value as loan. Interest 8.5% - 14%. Tenure 6 months to 3 years. No CIBIL required.</p>
    
    <div class="example-box">
      <b>Gold Loan Example:</b> 20g Gold @ ₹7500/g = ₹1,50,000 Value. 
      75% LTV = ₹1,12,500 Eligible Loan. 
      Take ₹1,00,000 at 9.5% for 12 months. EMI = ₹8,792. Total Interest = ₹5,504.
    </div>

    <h2 style="margin-top:20px;font-size:18px">5 Benefits of Gold Loan</h2>
    <div class="why-sip-grid">
