      <div class="why-item"><div class="num">2</div><p><b>Fast Approval:</b> Money in 30 minutes. Minimal documents. No CIBIL check.</p></div>
      <div class="why-item"><div class="num">3</div><p><b>High LTV:</b> RBI allows up to 75% of gold value as loan.</p></div>
      <div class="why-item"><div class="num">4</div><p><b>Flexible Repayment:</b> EMI, Interest-only, Bullet payment options available.</p></div>
      <div class="why-item"><div class="num">5</div><p><b>Safe Storage:</b> Bank keeps gold in locker. Insurance covered.</p></div>
    </div>
    <p><b>Key Insight:</b> Only 22K and 24K gold accepted. Purity matters. Compare SBI, HDFC, Muthoot, Manappuram for best rates.</p>

    <!-- DISCLAIMER -->
    <div class="disclaimer-box">
      <b>Disclaimer:</b> Gold rates change daily. LTV max 75% as per RBI. Interest rates vary by bank and tenure. This calculator is for estimation only.
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 5. GOLD LOAN GUIDE -->
  <div class="guide-box">
    <h2>Want to Learn More About Gold Loan?</h2>
    <p>Read our complete guide on gold loan eligibility, documents, LTV rules and best banks for gold loan.</p>
    <a href="gold-loan-guide.html" class="guide-btn">📖 Read Complete Gold Loan Guide</a>
  </div>

  <!-- 6. MORE CALCULATORS - TUMHARE BANAYE HUE -->
  <div class="card">
